    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Mobile Safari on iOS 6 (iPhone 4) has the very same problem: I cannot click to edit an Markdown/Text/Formula cell. Python code works. Additionally, there is no \"cmd\" or \"ctrl\" button on the iOS keyboard.\n\nAs the scrolling performance on iOS of is also not very good, I'd suggest a \"mobile\" version of the notebook-website with an \"edit\" and \"run\" button popping up next to selected cells.\n"
